  Chosen Development Model: Agile (Scrum)
The Agile model was chosen because it allows flexibility and continuous improvement during development. Since the YouthALB platform involves multiple features (user accounts, event browsing, reservations, admin management).
Agile helps the team:
Adapt to changing requirements
Deliver features in small, manageable iterations (sprints)
Continuously test and improve the system.
