User Stories (WHAT they need and WHY):
As a user, I want to register an account so that I can access the platform features.
As a user, I want to log in securely so that I can manage my reservations.
As a user, I want to browse events so that I can discover nightlife activities.
As a user, I want to filter events by location, date, and category so that I can find relevant events quickly.
As a user, I want to view event details so that I can decide whether to attend.
As a user, I want to reserve tickets so that I can secure my spot.
As a user, I want to receive a confirmation message so that I know my reservation is successful.
As a user, I want to see my reservation history so that I can track my bookings.
As a user, I want to cancel a reservation so that I can manage my plans.
As an admin, I want to create events so that users can see available activities.

Functional Requirements:
The system shall allow user registration.
The system shall allow user login and logout.
The system shall validate user credentials.
The system shall allow password reset.
The system shall display available events.
The system shall allow filtering by location.
The system shall allow filtering by date.
The system shall allow filtering by category.
The system shall display detailed event information.
The system shall allow ticket reservation.
The system shall check ticket availability before reservation.
The system shall generate a unique ticket number.
The system shall send reservation confirmation.
The system shall store user reservation history.
The system shall allow users to cancel reservations.
The system shall update available tickets after reservation/cancellation.
The system shall allow admins to create events.
The system shall allow admins to edit events.
The system shall allow admins to delete events.
